  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350°F.",
    "Mix almond slices and chopped dates with lemon juice and honey. Place in a baking dish and bake for 20 minutes until golden brown.",
    "Meanwhile, heat oil in a pan over medium-high heat. Add minced garlic and diced onion; sauté until softened, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add bell pepper to the pan and cook for another minute. Stir in almond mixture from the baking dish and continue cooking for 5 more minutes or until heated through.",
    "Remove from heat and serve hot."
